DRY RUN SHORTCUT  (for quick verification)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  Input: [1, 2, 3, 4]

  Prefix → [1, 1, 2, 6]

  Suffix pass:
  i=3: 6×1=6    (×4→suf=4)
  i=2: 2×4=8    (×3→suf=12)
  i=1: 1×12=12  (×2→suf=24)
  i=0: 1×24=24  (×1→suf=24)

  Output → [24, 12, 8, 6] ✅